		<div class="comment-avatar-wrap alignleft"><img alt src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccf682bfc2232c1e7aa5612f3ce95961?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" class="avatar avatar-50 photo jetpack-lazy-image" height="50" width="50" data-lazy-srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccf682bfc2232c1e7aa5612f3ce95961?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x" data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccf682bfc2232c1e7aa5612f3ce95961?s=50&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccf682bfc2232c1e7aa5612f3ce95961?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccf682bfc2232c1e7aa5612f3ce95961?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' /></noscript></div>					<div class="commenter_name">
						<a href='http://selfemployedsinglemum.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Emma</a>					</div>
					<p>Sarah &#8211; I hear you. It&#8217;s flippin&#8217; tough, and there&#8217;s no easy option. And yes, it&#8217;s a shock after years of hard work to find you&#8217;re cast aside simply because you chose to give birth to another human being. Choose yourself. Choose your family. Choose what feels good. and ps. while this site is called Self-Employed SINGLE Mum because I am one, the content applies equally to all mums &#8211; or to anyone else who wants more from life than life as an employee has to offer. Thank you so much for reading and commenting, I really appreciate it.</p>
